          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", but this is a great time to evaluate how dependent you are on the existing social platforms. And then you need to start building exit strategies that help you build closer relationships with readers, rather than just helping them follow you on other platforms.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
