          "description": "After a quiet decade, we’re finally seeing some innovation in the RSS space, and the old school blogger in me is delighted.",
          "author": "Adam Tinworth",
          "publisher": "One Man & His Blog",
          "thumbnail": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/10/adders_the_RSS_feed_icon_flying_throught_the_sky_d4ae1860-cdc1-4481-b13d-8bdc9a10f4fc.png",
